Package: ggspectra
Type: Package
Title: Plotting of Spectral Data
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Pedro J. Aphalo [aut, cre]
Maintainer: Pedro J. Aphalo <pedro.aphalo@helsinki.fi>
Description: This package provides additional annotations, stats and
